---
title: Pub Style Shrimp Cocktail with Cheesy Potato Rounds
description: Butter poached shrimp get the perfect dipper of cocktail sauce for the adults and ketchup for the kids! It's a pub night classic paired with restaurant inspired cheesy potato rounds!
